	 	 	 	 HEADLINE 
Ajay Devgn to shoot for Kapil Sharma’s show
	 	 	 	 CONTENT 
Ajay Devgn, who is making the TV rounds to promote his upcoming film Raid, will soon be going on the sets of Kapil Sharma’s new show Family Time With Kapil Sharma. Sources say that the superstar has already shot for a promo with the stand-up comedian, which is lively and funny.

“Ajay has gone to Delhi with the team of Raid to promote the film, but once he is back, he will shoot for the show. He is slated to shoot the episode on March 13,” informs a source.

Wonder if it will be the inaugural episode of Kapil’s show that will start airing from March 25.
